But you know what? I'm weak too. I

making constipated noises all day?

stuff that happened with Echo and

up.

...Right. Yeah!

See, Sho? That was a case of
yearning for friendship, not
constipation.
132:
What the hell was all that moping
around for then? She should've just
let it all out!
137:
Pythica's got her own way of doing

147:
Pythica... We were just looking for
you. Do you want to get crepes
156: I want to learn more about you both!

162:
Good times and bad! I'll be by your
side!

very beginning.
177:
Even though I didn't try to
understand you before
 I know now that I love

M-me too... No matter how much or
how little we have in common...

I must be the luckiest gal in the

226:

Along the way, I'll figure out more

So we can all be happy and healthy
together!
